instructions: put the plate on top of the charger
Put the napkin on top of the plate
put the dinner fork on the left hand side of the plate
put the salad fork on the left outter side of the dinner fork
put the dinner knife on the right hand side of the charger
put the tea spoon on the right outter most side of the dinner knife
put the soup spoon on the outter right side of the tea spoon
place the water glass above the dinner knife
place the wine glass above the tea spoon
place the wine glass between the first wine glass placed and the tea spoon
place the coffee cup on the right hand side of the last wine glass placed
place the bread plate above the dinner fork on the left
place the butter knife on top of the bread plate pointing at the wine glasses
put the dessert fork above the napkin facing the wine glasses
face the dessert spoon between the dessert fork and charger facing the bread plate
